  "title": "Operation Coordinator",
  "description": "<p><u><strong>Roles and Responsibilities:</strong></u></p>\n<p>Order Processing: </p>\n<p>Manage procurement requests, handle purchase orders, verify order accuracy, and coordinate with customers/internal stakeholders to ensure timely delivery.</p>\n<p>Claims Processing: </p>\n<p>Collaborate with the team to handle all types of claims, ensuring proper documentation, follow-up, and resolution, while maintaining confidentiality and accuracy.</p>\n<p>General Office </p>\n<p>Support: Maintain and organize physical and electronic filing systems for quick retrieval of information. Work with different departments to support various administrative and operational activities.</p>\n<p>Coordinate meetings, prepare agendas, and take minutes when needed.</p>\n<p><u><strong>Additional Responsibilities:</strong></u></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Maintains office supplies and furniture, ensuring availability and functionality.</li>\n  <li>Support event planning and logistics for company functions or team activities.</li>\n  <li>Data entry and basic analysis to support reporting and decision-making.</li>\n  <li>Coordinate with customers/internal stakeholders to ensure timely delivery.</li>\n  <li>Managing the key stakeholders’ calendar, scheduling meetings and preparing briefing materials.</li>\n  <li>Handling correspondence and organizing travel arrangements to ensure smooth daily operation.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><u><strong>Requirements:</strong></u></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>High school diploma or Bachelor's degree with fields like business administration or operations management.</li>\n  <li>Previous experience in an administrative, office management, or operations role will a plus. </li>\n  <li>Good interpersonal abilities for collaborating with different departments.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><br></p>",
